                    UMS Login Guide 1.1 (18.05.96)

      Guidelines on a uniform login-procedure in UMS applications

                    by Ralf Garbade and Olaf Peters

This document describes a standard for starting applications under the
Universal Message System (UMS), either from commandline or a graphical
user interface GUI). This document applies to the Amiga implementation
of UMS(1).


